</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_224" id="112r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_224_r2l2"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hadmarn dem <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l3"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu laber </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_224_r2l4">Edler <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vns ewr Edell <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l6">hat / euch vnſer erber botſchafft cʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough">leihen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_224_r2l5">ſchicken </ab></add> auf den tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l7">gen Sulcʒbach auf den nechſten Suntag nach ſant Mıchels </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l8">tag cʒunacht daʒu ſein / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l9">wollen das alſo <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tun / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / ob icht darein viel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l10">alſo das derſelb 
<add><ab facs="#facs_224_line_1573027548623_127">tag </ab></add> abe geen vvürd / daʒ Jr vns das <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ſo Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l13">cʒeitlichſt 
<del rend="strikethrough">vor </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_224_line_1573027567094_139">mügt </ab></add> wiſſen laſſen wollet / daʒ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht v̈mb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l14">ſuſt <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Edell / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l15"><expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Mathei / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_224" id="112r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hadmarn dem <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n,</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu Laber </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler, <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr edell
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, euch unser erber botschafft czu
                            <add>schicken</add> auf den tag gen Sulczbach, auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">nechsten suntag nach sant Michels
                                tag</q>06.10.1415</note>
</app> czu nacht da zu sein, das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und wollen das also
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tun. Und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> ob icht darein viel, also das derselb
                            <add>tag</add> abegeen würd, daz ir uns das
                        <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>, so ir czeitlichst <add>mügt</add>, wissen
                        lassen wollet, daz die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht ümb sust
                                <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Mathei. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
